  "texts": [
    "This novel approach signifies substantial progress in traffic control systems, possibly resolving current urban mobility difficulties.",
    "The contribution of this research is as follows:• Focusing on specific benchmark methods to ensure successful traffic reduction implementation for enhancing a traffic-free smart city.",
    "• Applying advanced, customized layer based method for making efficient traffic reduction.• Developing an advanced DQN to maintain the traffic reduction system in an intersection.• Performing RL technique of state, action, and rewards successfully in the traffic reduction domain.• Focusing on minimizing queue length and increasing rewards at each length.",
    "Organization of the paperThe research is divided into multiple areas, each with a specific function.",
    "Section \"Related work\" summarizes relevant literature on the topic and serves as the basis for the investigation."
